## 📊 Agent Weights (Dynamic)

Weights auto-adjust based on prediction accuracy:

| Агент | Base Weight | Boost Factor | Accuracy Weighting |
|-------|-------------|--------------|-------------------|
| MarketAnalyst | 0.20 | 0.5-2.0x | High |
| BullResearcher | 0.10 | 0.5-2.0x | Medium |
| BearResearcher | 0.10 | 0.5-2.0x | Medium |
| Andrews | 0.15 | 0.5-2.0x | High |
| DowTheory | 0.10 | 0.5-2.0x | Medium |
| Gann | 0.10 | 0.5-2.0x | Medium |
| Astrologer | 0.15 | 0.5-2.0x | High |
| CycleAgent | 0.10 | 0.5-2.0x | Low |

