## 🧠 Self-Learning Loop

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    FEEDBACK LOOP                            │
│                                                             │
│   1. Agent makes prediction                                 │
│      └─► Stored in Prediction Tracker                       │
│                                                             │
│   2. After timeframe (e.g., 24h)                           │
│      └─► Outcome resolved (correct/partial/wrong)          │
│                                                             │
│   3. Agent weight updated                                   │
│      └─► Accuracy-based rebalancing                        │
│                                                             │
│   4. Pattern learned (if consistent)                       │
│      └─► Stored in ChromaDB patterns collection             │
│                                                             │
│   5. Next analysis uses updated weights                     │
│      └─► Better signal synthesis                           │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

