## 💾 Persistent Memory (ChromaDB)

### Collections:

| Collection | Purpose | Indexing |
|------------|---------|----------|
| `analysis` | Past agent analyses | symbol, agent, signal |
| `feedback` | User feedback | agent_id, rating |
| `outcomes` | Prediction outcomes | symbol, direction |
| `patterns` | Learned patterns | pattern_type, confidence |

### RAG Pipeline:

```
Query → Embed → ChromaDB → Similar Results → Context → LLM → Response
```

