## 🚀 Запуск v2.1

### Option 1: Docker Compose
```bash
docker-compose up -d
```

### Option 2: Manual
```bash
# Terminal 1: API Backend
cd api && uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000

# Terminal 2: React UI
cd ui_react && npm install && npm run dev

# Terminal 3: Start agents
python -m agents.orchestrator
```

